# Project Map

> Directory structure with explanations. Updated by project-architect.

## Top-Level
```
.
├── .claude/              # Claude Code config, agents, commands
├── .github/              # GitHub Actions, templates
├── app/ (or src/)        # Application source
├── components/           # Shared UI components
├── docs/                 # Documentation
├── lib/                  # Utilities, helpers, clients
├── public/               # Static assets
├── supabase/             # Database migrations, seeds, functions
├── tests/                # Test files
├── types/                # TypeScript type definitions
├── .env.example          # Required env vars (template)
├── CLAUDE.md             # Entry point for Claude Code
├── package.json          # Dependencies and scripts
├── tsconfig.json         # TypeScript config
└── README.md             # Project intro and setup
```

## Key Directories

### `app/` (Next.js App Router)
- `(auth)/` — public auth pages (login, signup)
- `(dashboard)/` — authenticated dashboard
- `api/` — API route handlers
- `b/[slug]/` — public booking pages
- `layout.tsx` — root layout with providers
- `globals.css` — global styles and CSS variables

### `components/`
- `ui/` — shadcn/ui primitives (Button, Input, Dialog)
- `forms/` — form components
- `layout/` — navigation, headers, sidebars
- `features/` — feature-specific components

### `lib/`
- `supabase/` — Supabase client and helpers
- `utils.ts` — general utilities
- `validators/` — Zod schemas
- `api/` — API client wrappers
- `hooks/` — custom React hooks

### `supabase/`
- `migrations/` — SQL migration files (timestamped)
- `seed.sql` — development seed data
- `functions/` — Edge Functions
- `config.toml` — Supabase config

### `docs/`
- `ARCHITECTURE.md` — system design and decisions
- `DATABASE.md` — schema, RLS, indexes
- `CONVENTIONS.md` — coding standards
- `GOTCHAS.md` — known pitfalls
- `SECURITY.md` — threat model
- `ADR/` — Architecture Decision Records

## Where to Put New Code

| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| New page | `app/[route]/page.tsx` |
| New API route | `app/api/[route]/route.ts` |
| New UI primitive | `components/ui/` |
| New feature component | `components/features/[feature]/` |
| New database table | `supabase/migrations/[timestamp]_[name].sql` |
| New utility | `lib/utils.ts` or `lib/[domain]/` |
| New hook | `lib/hooks/` |
| New type | `types/[domain].ts` |
| New test | Co-located with file (`*.test.ts`) |
| New E2E test | `tests/e2e/[flow].spec.ts` |

## Import Aliases
- `@/` → project root
- `@/components` → `./components`
- `@/lib` → `./lib`
- `@/types` → `./types`
